korean:
  title: 수
  author: 을지문덕
  language: kor
  text: |-
    신책은 천문을 꿰뚫었고
    묘산은 지리에 통달했네
    싸움에 이겨 공이 이미 높거니
    족함을 알아 원컨대 그치시라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_010_0010&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 족함을 …… 그치시라 : '
    value: 노자(老子)의 《도덕경(道德經)》에, “족함을 알면 욕되지 않고, 그칠 줄 알면 위태롭지 않다 [知足不辱 知止不殆].”란 말이 있다.
english:
  title: On Sui
  author: Eulji Mundeok
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Divine strategy pierces through the celestial patterns,
    Subtle calculation penetrates earthly forms.
    Victory in battle has brought glory already high—
    Knowing sufficiency, I pray we now cease.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: 'The closing couplet alludes to the Daodejing: ''He who knows when to stop does not find himself in trouble; he who knows when to stop shall live long.'' The poet invokes this Daoist wisdom to counsel restraint and moderation in the aftermath of triumph.'
